<p>
<note n="0075002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075002">Śikṣāsamuccaya.</note>
<note n="0075003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075003">梵 Śāntideva.（寂天）</note>
<note n="0075004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075004">（（西天…譯））三十五字＝（（宋西天三藏銀青光錄大夫試光錄卿普明慈覺傳梵大師法護等奉詔譯））二十九字【明】</note>
<note n="0075005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075005">Dānapāramitā prathamaḥ paricchedaḥ.</note>
<note n="0075006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075006">Gaṇḍavyūha-sūtra.</note>
<note n="0075007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075007">Ratnolkā-dhāraṇī.</note>
<note n="0075008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075008">得＝能【明】</note>
<note n="0076001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076001">生＝類【明】</note>
<note n="0076002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076002">Daśadharma-sūtra.</note>
